## 11. ANTI-PATTERNS TO AVOID

- ❌ Manual infrastructure changes (use Terraform)
- ❌ Hardcoded secrets
- ❌ Single instance (use Multi-AZ)
- ❌ No monitoring or logging
- ❌ No backups
- ❌ No disaster recovery plan
- ❌ Over-provisioned resources
- ❌ No cost tracking
- ❌ No auto-scaling
- ❌ Manual deployments

